    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been super well-loved. If you're looking for a reliable car that still looks sharp on the road, this is the one for you! I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 29500.0,
