    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. This unit is equipped with the Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. Significant mechanical stewardship has been performed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and rod bearing replacement to mitigate common S54 failure points. The chassis has been enhanced with reinforced subframe mounts and polyurethane bushings to maintain torsional rigidity. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic patina typical of a well-loved performance machine, the powertrain remains exceptionally healthy, delivering linear torque and precise throttle response. This is a mechanically sorted example ready for spirited B-road duty.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
